name: DisplayPort to DVI Single link Cable - 6 ft | Dell USA
description: The DisplayPort to DVI Single link Cable from Tripp® Lite allows you to connect a computer with a DisplayPort connection, to a HDTV or Computer Monitor with a DVI connection. This link cable allows PC images to be dispalyed on big screen HDTV orcomputer monitors with DVI. It also supports full 1080p video resolution while passing through Digital Video signals. Furthermore, this cable features fully molded ends to ensure long life enjoyment just for you.
